## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Any modern web browser
- Git (optional, for cloning)

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/HimaTech-Store.git

# Navigate to project
cd HimaTech-Store

# Open in browser (or use Live Server)
open index.html